<p>The <code>true</code> tag always executes its content (condition always true).</p>

<h2>Basic True</h2>
<pre>{open}true{close}
  This always displays
{open}/true{close}</pre>
{true}
<p style="color:green">This always displays</p>
{/true}

<h2>True with Else</h2>
<pre>{open}true{close}
  True branch
{open}else{close}
  Never shown
{open}/true{close}</pre>
{true}
<p>True branch (else never executes)</p>
{else}
<p>Never shown</p>
{/true}

<h2>Nested True for Scoping</h2>
<pre>{open}true{close}
  {open}set $local = 'inner value'{close}
  Inside: {open}$local{close}
{open}/true{close}</pre>
{true}
  {set $local = 'inner value'}
  <p>Inside: {$local}</p>
{/true}
